{"tid":1445852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒: 黑警可能假扮示威者做「過火行為」","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:35:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"668a1a1b5e75526f184b6181daef44b2caf096e6","tid":1445852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/2412692735489887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F2412692735489887&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=15ca3587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/2412692735489887</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n14分鐘 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n黑警假扮示威者拘捕示威者，賤過地底泥。<br />\n<br />\n既然你哋都明刀明槍假扮示威者，諗住咁樣可以更加容易拘捕示威者，唔好怪香港人根本唔會再相信真示威者做過任何過火嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n你以為咁樣拘捕拉得好爽，但任何被認為係嘅過火行為，過去或者未來，都好自然咁樣會被覺得係由黑警假扮嘅示威者去策動，無論幾多影片或者相片泉源，都唔再能夠證實任何舉動必然係由貨真價實嘅示威者做。"},{"pid":"63e0df392a64c185e0e817bd816cffda952fedd2","tid":1445852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad87a1749896994436ea7dd777d90cd5c43a7a31","tid":1445852,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aced8558cfe77ef45a07bc27c0f966a424f26c5","tid":1445852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k